column5: Hey folks.  I made a video of some of our spring fishing.  The bite started slow and spring was late but we managed the best we could and as always put some fish in the canoe. https://vimeo.com/67742598
Niiicely done.  That is some great footage
nice video ... did you have a Souris River canoe ?
Good choice on the Crosswinds. Nice fish too!
Loved it Sal.  Whats the band called in the  first song? Great tune.
the first song is by G Love!  Scott Kevlar
